ed determination of temperatures and\nspectral classification of the cool companions will be presented in a\nforthcoming work.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Jan 2016 18:12:08 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 21 Jan 2016 16:08:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-01"}
