 experiments. Overall, the results of this work\nhighlight the importance of kinetic processes in the defect physics of\nmetastable materials, and provide a framework that can be applied when\nconsidering the properties of such materials in general.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Jan 2016 19:46:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-25"}
